    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-09-29T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-09-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="345" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d345">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Adams</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1552.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-09-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 29, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                            despatch of the 14th instant, (No. 1044,) in regard to the visit of the
                            ex-Queen of the Sandwich Islands to England.</p>
                <p>While approving your vigilance in the matter, I have to request that you
                            will exercise your own discretion as to making suggestions to the effect
                            that we would not look with satisfaction upon any special change in the
                            attitude of the Hawaiian kingdom affecting its relations to the United
                            States.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Francis Adams</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
